---
---

<section class="py-32 md:py-48 px-6 bg-[#F9F8F6] dark:bg-[#1A1918]">
  <!-- Terminal Header -->
  <div class="font-mono text-xs md:text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-[#121212]/50 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
    &gt; SYS.DEPLOYMENT // THE_PROTOCOL
  </div>

  <!-- Headline -->
  <h2 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black uppercase italic tracking-tighter leading-[1.1] text-center text-[#121212] dark:text-[#EBE9E4] mb-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    How We Build<br />Your Moat.
  </h2>

  <!-- 3-Step Grid -->
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
    <!-- Card 01: Infrastructure & AI -->
    <div class="p-8 lg:p-10 border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 rounded-[2rem] bg-black/5 dark:bg-white/5 relative group hover:border-[#FF5733]/50 transition-colors duration-500">
      <div class="font-mono text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-[#121212]/20 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/20 mb-6 group-hover:text-[#FF5733] transition-colors duration-500">01</div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-[#121212] dark:text-[#EBE9E4] mb-4">Strategy & Architecture</h3>
      <p class="text-lg text-[#121212]/70 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/70 leading-relaxed">
        We audit your existing ecosystem and architect a custom blueprint matched to your actual operational capacity. This includes engineering new business models designed to <strong class="font-bold text-[#121212] dark:text-[#EBE9E4]">turn raw attention into a self-sustaining asset.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 02: Culture & Rituals -->
    <div class="p-8 lg:p-10 border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 rounded-[2rem] bg-black/5 dark:bg-white/5 relative group hover:border-[#FF5733]/50 transition-colors duration-500">
      <div class="font-mono text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-[#121212]/20 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/20 mb-6 group-hover:text-[#FF5733] transition-colors duration-500">02</div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-[#121212] dark:text-[#EBE9E4] mb-4">Supporting Systems</h3>
      <p class="text-lg text-[#121212]/70 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/70 leading-relaxed">
        A blueprint is only as good as the machine running it. We deploy the technical platforms, AI automations, and operational workflows required to support the vision, and then <strong class="font-bold text-[#121212] dark:text-[#EBE9E4]">train your team to operate the ecosystem flawlessly.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 03: Monetization & Scale -->
    <div class="p-8 lg:p-10 border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 rounded-[2rem] bg-black/5 dark:bg-white/5 relative group hover:border-[#FF5733]/50 transition-colors duration-500">
      <div class="font-mono text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-[#121212]/20 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/20 mb-6 group-hover:text-[#FF5733] transition-colors duration-500">03</div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-[#121212] dark:text-[#EBE9E4] mb-4">Culture & Scale</h3>
      <p class="text-lg text-[#121212]/70 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/70 leading-relaxed">
        We launch the environment and relentlessly measure the data. We validate the rituals directly with your community, refactoring the human feedback loops <strong class="font-bold text-[#121212] dark:text-[#EBE9E4]">so the culture scales predictably, with or without you.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Output Readout Block: Data Matrix -->
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto mt-24 lg:mt-32">

    <div class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-[#121212]/50 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/50 mb-6 flex items-center px-6">
      &gt; SYSTEM_OUTPUT // EXPECTED_ROI
    </div>

    <div class="border-y border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 bg-black/[0.02] dark:bg-white/[0.02]">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 divide-y lg:divide-y-0 lg:divide-x divide-black/10 dark:divide-white/10">

        <div class="p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col group hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors duration-300">
          <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-[#121212]/40 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/40 mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase">&gt; METRIC_01</span>
          <span class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-[#121212] dark:text-[#EBE9E4] uppercase tracking-tighter mb-3 group-hover:text-[#FF5733] transition-colors duration-300">Defensible Culture</span>
          <span class="text-sm md:text-base text-[#121212]/70 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/70 leading-relaxed">Zero reliance on algorithm churn. Your people stay for each other.</span>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col group hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors duration-300">
          <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-[#121212]/40 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/40 mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase">&gt; METRIC_02</span>
          <span class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-[#121212] dark:text-[#EBE9E4] uppercase tracking-tighter mb-3 group-hover:text-[#FF5733] transition-colors duration-300">Maximized LTV</span>
          <span class="text-sm md:text-base text-[#121212]/70 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/70 leading-relaxed">Members who stick around compound your retention and easily upgrade.</span>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col group hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors duration-300">
          <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-[#121212]/40 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/40 mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase">&gt; METRIC_03</span>
          <span class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-[#121212] dark:text-[#EBE9E4] uppercase tracking-tighter mb-3 group-hover:text-[#FF5733] transition-colors duration-300">Network Effects</span>
          <span class="text-sm md:text-base text-[#121212]/70 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/70 leading-relaxed">Organic, high-ticket referrals driven entirely by peer-to-peer advocacy.</span>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col group hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors duration-300">
          <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-[#121212]/40 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/40 mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase">&gt; METRIC_04</span>
          <span class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-[#121212] dark:text-[#EBE9E4] uppercase tracking-tighter mb-3 group-hover:text-[#FF5733] transition-colors duration-300">Predictable ARR</span>
          <span class="text-sm md:text-base text-[#121212]/70 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/70 leading-relaxed">A self-sustaining engine that compounds revenue without burning out the founder.</span>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
